comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.call_score_id is 'Surrogate integer key for this score row, generated by the ETL.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.call_id is 'Foreign key to Call_H.call_id. One score row exists per call where AI scoring was completed. Approximately 95,939 of 95,952 calls have scores.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.regulatory_obligations_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity (0-1) measuring agent coverage of regulatory obligations. 0 = behaviour absent;
 above 0.75 = strong alignment with reference rubric. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.privacy_disclosure_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent disclosed privacy/recording notice information. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.complaint_rights_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent informed the caller of their complaint and dispute rights. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.terms_and_conditions_explained_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring clarity and completeness of terms and conditions explanation. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.consent_gathering_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether explicit consent was sought before proceeding with account actions or data sharing. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.identity_verification_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the rigour and completeness of caller identity verification. A critical compliance metric;
 low scores indicate potential authentication gaps. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.account_access_verification_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether account access was properly verified before sensitive actions were taken. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.script_adherence_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring agent adherence to approved call scripts and talking points. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.fee_charge_disclosure_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether applicable fees and charges were clearly disclosed to the caller. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.avoidance_of_overpromise_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent avoided making commitments or promises beyond what the organisation can deliver. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.limitation_of_liability_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring appropriate acknowledgement of liability limitations. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.call_recording_disclosure_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent disclosed that the call was being recorded. Compliance category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.customer_centric_language_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring use of customer-first, inclusive language that focuses on the caller''s needs. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.reassurance_and_support_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring how effectively the agent reassured and supported the caller, particularly during uncertain or stressful situations. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.customer_appreciation_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring expressions of genuine gratitude and appreciation directed at the caller. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.empathetic_tone_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the warmth and empathetic tone maintained throughout the call. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.empathy_statements_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the use of explicit empathy statements (e.g. "I understand how frustrating that must be"). Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.positive_framing_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s tendency to frame responses positively (what can be done rather than what cannot). Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.avoiding_negativity_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring avoidance of negative language, blame, or dismissive phrasing. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.avoidance_of_blame_or_deflection_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent took ownership rather than deflecting responsibility to other teams or systems. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.apology_or_regret_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the appropriate and sincere use of apologies or expressions of regret where warranted. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.respectful_language_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring consistent use of respectful, professional language throughout the call. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.personalisation_contextualisation_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s use of caller-specific context (name, account history, prior interactions) to personalise the conversation. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.frustration_acknowledgement_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent explicitly acknowledged caller frustration before attempting resolution. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.brand_aligned_tone_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring alignment of the agent''s language and tone with the brand voice guidelines. Customer Experience category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.active_listening_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring observable active listening behaviours such as paraphrasing, affirming, and summarising caller input. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.avoiding_interruptions_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s avoidance of interrupting the caller mid-sentence or mid-thought. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.turn_taking_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring balanced, orderly turn-taking throughout the dialogue. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.clarification_questions_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the effective use of clarifying questions to ensure mutual understanding. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.appropriate_questioning_technique_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the use of open, closed, and probing questions at contextually appropriate moments. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.concise_explanations_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether explanations were delivered concisely without unnecessary repetition or verbosity. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.avoiding_jargon_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s avoidance of technical jargon or industry terms that the caller may not understand. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.process_explanation_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the clarity and completeness of process explanations provided to the caller. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.structured_signposting_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the use of clear signposting phrases to guide the caller through the conversation structure. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.repetition_for_emphasis_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the strategic use of repetition to reinforce key information. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.confirmation_of_understanding_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent confirmed the caller''s understanding of key information before proceeding. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.reframing_or_simplification_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s ability to reframe complex information in simpler terms when the caller showed confusion. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.pacing_and_flow_control_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring natural pacing and smooth conversational flow throughout the call. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.avoiding_filler_or_uncertainty_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s avoidance of filler words (um, uh, like) and phrases that project uncertainty. Communication Quality category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.resolution_confirmation_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent explicitly confirmed the resolution with the caller before closing. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.action_commitment_next_steps_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the clarity and specificity of any action commitments or next steps communicated to the caller. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.wrap_up_summary_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the quality and completeness of the call wrap-up summary provided before closing. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.case_logging_notetaking_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent verbally confirmed that the interaction was being logged or noted for follow-up. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.order_placement_modification_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the accuracy and completeness of order placement or modification actions confirmed during the call. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.ownership_and_accountability_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s demonstration of personal ownership and accountability for the caller''s issue. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.time_estimation_sla_mention_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether realistic timeframes or SLA commitments were communicated to the caller. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.status_update_progress_report_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent proactively provided status updates or progress reports during longer interactions. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.time_awareness_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s sensitivity to call duration and appropriate management of time. Call Handling category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.de_escalation_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the effectiveness of de-escalation techniques used when the caller was distressed or hostile. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.calm_under_pressure_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s composure and professional demeanour under difficult call conditions. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.confidence_and_reassurance_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s projection of confidence and ability to reassure the caller about the outcome. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.confidence_building_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring specific confidence-building language used to increase caller trust in the agent and organisation. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.internal_handoff_transfer_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the quality of internal handoff or transfer execution, including warm transfer protocols and caller briefing. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.escalation_to_higher_tier_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the appropriateness and quality of escalations to senior agents or supervisors. Conduct and Professionalism category. High values correlate with difficult or complex calls.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.billing_and_payment_discussion_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the accuracy and sensitivity of billing or payment discussions. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.call_control_direction_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the agent''s ability to steer the conversation purposefully without being dismissive of the caller. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.call_purpose_disclosure_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring whether the agent clearly stated the purpose of an outbound call or confirmed the purpose of an inbound call at the outset. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_DOM_STD_T}}.Call_Score_H.technical_troubleshooting_avg_sim is 'Average cosine similarity score measuring the effectiveness and structure of technical troubleshooting steps performed during the call. Conduct and Professionalism category.';

